    <p>{`Please refer to the `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "/testrunner-toolkit/configuration#common-syntax-reference"
      }}>{`Common Configuration Syntax Reference`}</a>{`for information regarding fields such as `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`apiVersion`}</inlineCode>{`, `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`kind`}</inlineCode>{`, and `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`sauce`}</inlineCode>{`.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "example-configuration"
    }}>{`Example Configuration`}</h2>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-yaml"
      }}>{`apiVersion: v1alpha
kind: cypress
sauce:
  region: us-west-1
  metadata:
    name: Testing Cypress Support
    tags:
      - e2e
      - release team
      - other tag
    build: Release $CI_COMMIT_SHORT_SHA
docker:
  fileTransfer: mount
cypress:
  configFile: "tests/cypress.json"  # We determine related files based on the location of the config file.
  version: 5.6.0
suites:
  - name: "saucy test"
    browser: "chrome"
    browserVersion: "latest" # Can also be a hardcoded version
    screenResolution: "1920x1080"
    config:
      env:
        hello: world
      testFiles: [ "**/*.*" ] # Cypress native glob support.
`}</code></pre>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "cypress"
    }}><inlineCode parentName="h2">{`cypress`}</inlineCode></h2>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Description`}</strong>{`: Details specific to the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`cypress`}</inlineCode>{` configuration.`}</p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Type`}</strong>{`: `}<em parentName="p">{`object`}</em></p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Example`}</strong>{`:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-yaml"
      }}>{`cypress:
  configFile: "cypress.json"
`}</code></pre>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "configfile"
    }}><inlineCode parentName="h3">{`configFile`}</inlineCode></h3>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Description`}</strong>{`: The designated `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`cypress`}</inlineCode>{` configuration file. `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`saucectl`}</inlineCode>{` determines related files based on the location of the config file. By default `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`saucectl`}</inlineCode>{` defers to the test file location defined in `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`cypress.json`}</inlineCode>{`.`}</p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Type`}</strong>{`: `}<em parentName="p">{`string`}</em></p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Example`}</strong>{`:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-yaml"
      }}>{`  configFile: "cypress.json"
`}</code></pre>
    <blockquote>
      <p parentName="blockquote">{`For further information regarding cypress configurations, please consult the `}<a parentName="p" {...{
          "href": "https://docs.cypress.io/guides/references/configuration.html#Options"
        }}>{`Cypress documentation`}</a>{`.`}</p>
    </blockquote>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "record"
    }}><inlineCode parentName="h3">{`record`}</inlineCode></h3>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Description`}</strong>{`: Record video of tests running.`}</p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Type`}</strong>{`: `}<em parentName="p">{`boolean`}</em></p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Example`}</strong>{`:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-yaml"
      }}>{`  record: true
  key: $MY_SECRET_KEY
`}</code></pre>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "key"
    }}><inlineCode parentName="h3">{`key`}</inlineCode></h3>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Description`}</strong>{`: Secret record key.`}</p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Type`}</strong>{`: `}<em parentName="p">{`string`}</em></p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Example`}</strong>{`:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-yaml"
      }}>{`  record: true
  key: $MY_SECRET_KEY
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`In order for the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`record`}</inlineCode>{` and `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`key`}</inlineCode>{` fields to work you must add the cypress `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`"projectId"`}</inlineCode>{` in your `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`cypress.json`}</inlineCode>{` file. `}</p>
    <p>{`The value of your `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`projectId`}</inlineCode>{` correlates directly with the value of the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`key`}</inlineCode>{` field; in this case `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`$MY_SECRET_KEY`}</inlineCode>{`.`}</p>
    <blockquote>
      <p parentName="blockquote">{`Please refer to `}<a parentName="p" {...{
          "href": "https://docs.cypress.io/guides/dashboard/projects.html#Project-ID"
        }}>{`this Cypress Documentation page`}</a>{` for further information about how to configure/retrieve the cypress `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`projectId`}</inlineCode>{`.`}</p>
      <p parentName="blockquote">{`For more information about the cypress `}<strong parentName="p">{`Record Key`}</strong>{`, please consult this `}<a parentName="p" {...{
          "href": "https://docs.cypress.io/guides/guides/command-line.html#cypress-run-record-key-lt-record-key-gt"
        }}>{`Cypress Documentation page`}</a>{`.`}</p>
    </blockquote>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "suites"
    }}><inlineCode parentName="h2">{`suites`}</inlineCode></h2>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Description`}</strong>{`: Field for defining test suite details such as the suite `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`name`}</inlineCode>{`, desired `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`browser`}</inlineCode>{`
/ `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`platformName`}</inlineCode>{`, and `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`config`}</inlineCode>{`.`}</p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Type`}</strong>{`: `}<em parentName="p">{`object`}</em></p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Example`}</strong>{`:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-yaml"
      }}>{`suites:
  - name: "saucy test"
    browser: "chrome"
    browserVersion: "latest"
    config:
      env:
        hello: world
      testFiles: [ "**/*.*" ] # Cypress native glob support.
`}</code></pre>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "name"
    }}><inlineCode parentName="h3">{`name`}</inlineCode></h3>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Description`}</strong>{`: Name of the test suite.`}</p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Type`}</strong>{`: `}<em parentName="p">{`string`}</em></p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Example`}</strong>{`:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-yaml"
      }}>{`  - name: "saucy test"
`}</code></pre>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "browser"
    }}><inlineCode parentName="h3">{`browser`}</inlineCode></h3>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Description`}</strong>{`: Name of the browser in which the test runs.`}</p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Type`}</strong>{`: `}<em parentName="p">{`string`}</em></p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Example`}</strong>{`:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-yaml"
      }}>{`    browser: "chrome"
`}</code></pre>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "browserversion"
    }}><inlineCode parentName="h3">{`browserVersion`}</inlineCode></h3>
    <p><small><Highlight color="#ad1415" mdxType="Highlight">sauce cloud only</Highlight></small><a href="/testrunner-toolkit/running-tests#test-on-sauce-labs">ℹ</a></p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Description`}</strong>{`: Version of the browser in which the test runs.`}</p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Type`}</strong>{`: `}<em parentName="p">{`string`}</em></p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Example`}</strong>{`:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-yaml"
      }}>{`    browserVersion: "85.0"
`}</code></pre>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "platformname"
    }}><inlineCode parentName="h3">{`platformName`}</inlineCode></h3>
    <p><small><Highlight color="#ad1415" mdxType="Highlight">sauce cloud only</Highlight></small><a href="/testrunner-toolkit/running-tests#test-on-sauce-labs">ℹ</a></p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Description`}</strong>{`: Operating system on which the browser and test runs.`}</p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Type`}</strong>{`: `}<em parentName="p">{`string`}</em></p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Example`}</strong>{`:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-yaml"
      }}>{`    platformName: "Windows 10"
`}</code></pre>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "screenresolution"
    }}><inlineCode parentName="h3">{`screenResolution`}</inlineCode></h3>
    <p><small><Highlight color="#ad1415" mdxType="Highlight">sauce cloud only</Highlight></small><a href="/testrunner-toolkit/running-tests#test-on-sauce-labs">ℹ</a></p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Description`}</strong>{`: Field where you can change the browser window screen resolution.`}</p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Type`}</strong>{`: `}<em parentName="p">{`string`}</em></p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Example`}</strong>{`:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-yaml"
      }}>{`    screenResolution: "1920x1080"
`}</code></pre>
    <blockquote>
      <p parentName="blockquote">{`For all available resolutions please visit `}<a parentName="p" {...{
          "href": "https://wiki.saucelabs.com/display/DOCS/Test+Configuration+Options#TestConfigurationOptions-SauceLabsCustomTestingOptions"
        }}>{`this documentation page`}</a>{`.`}</p>
    </blockquote>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "config"
    }}><inlineCode parentName="h3">{`config`}</inlineCode></h3>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Description`}</strong>{`: Details specific to the test configuration, for example: `}</p>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul"><inlineCode parentName="li">{`testFiles`}</inlineCode>{` ( `}<em parentName="li">{`string array`}</em>{` | `}<em parentName="li">{`string`}</em>{` | `}<em parentName="li">{`regex`}</em>{` ): the specific location of test files`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul"><inlineCode parentName="li">{`env`}</inlineCode>{` ( `}<em parentName="li">{`string`}</em>{` | `}<em parentName="li">{`int`}</em>{` | `}<em parentName="li">{`float`}</em>{` | `}<em parentName="li">{`boolean`}</em>{` ) any ephemeral/environment variables.`}</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Type`}</strong>{`: `}<em parentName="p">{`object`}</em></p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Example`}</strong>{`:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-yaml"
      }}>{`    config:
      env:
        hello: world
      testFiles: [ "**/*.*" ]
`}</code></pre>
    </MDXLayout>;
}

;
